    "summary": {
      "value": "Sacrifice HP for massive damage."
    },
    "description": "<p><strong>Requirements:</strong> you must have mastered the <strong>Darkblade</strong> Class.</p><hr /><p>When you hit a creature with an attack, if that attack <strong>only</strong> targeted that creature and you have a <strong>Bond</strong> towards them, you may choose to spend half of your current Hit Points, rounded down. If you do, the attack deals extra damage equal to <strong>【10 multiplied by the strength of your Bond towards the target】</strong>.</p><p>You may use this Skill only on your turn during a conflict, and <strong>only once per turn</strong>.</p><hr /><p><strong>Target Suffers:</strong> @DMG[10 untyped]{1 Bond: 10 Untyped}, @DMG[20 untyped]{2 Bond: 20 Untyped}, or @DMG[30 untyped]{3 Bond: 30 Untyped}</p>",
